                  Relations between the several powers of the State.
               </item>
               <item>
                  <label>5.</label>
                  The Evolution of the State (beginning with Greece,<lb/> since
                  all, with us, begins with Greece).
               </item>
               <item>
                  <label>6.</label>
                  An Economic Theory in Politics.
               </item>
               <item>
                  <label>7.</label>
                  The Social Importance of Spelling.
