            <div>
               <head><hi rend="underline">Political Sociology.</hi></head>
               <p>Since there is no social science, that is to say,<lb/> no sociology, it may seem
                  strange that any book should<lb/> be entitled Political Sociology – a title
                     expressing<lb/><del rend="overtyped">the</del>a species of an unexistent
                  genus.</p>
            </div>
